1. *Ona* *laži* kada govori o svojim uspesima. (She lies when she talks about her successes.)
2. On je cini se stalno u *lažima*. (He seems to be constantly in lies.)
3. Njen brat je talentovan za *lažiranje*. (Her brother is talented in lying.)
4. *Laži* su za nju postale navika. (Lying had become a habit for her.)
5. Ne verujem u ono što govoriš, to su sve *laži*. (I don't believe what you are saying, it's all lies.)